                          int iAbsoluteEnd,
                          String iIsoformID,
                          double iWeight,
                          int iColor)
Instantiates a new Rectangle_Weighted.

Parameters:
iScaledXCoord - the left value of the X coordinate of the rectangle
iScaledLength - the scaled length of the rectangle
iScaledHeight - the height of the rectangle
iAbsoluteStart - the genomic coordinate of the start of the region defined by the rectangle
iAbsoluteEnd - the genomic coordinate of the end of the region defined by the rectangle
iIsoformID - the ID of the MRNA that this is a part of
iWeight - the weight of the rectangle (should represent the average number of short reads that span its region)
iColor - the color of the rectangle
